sap.app.title: The SAPUI5 library contains classes that are mainly used in smart template applications, but can also be used in any Fiori/UI5 application that uses the OData protocol to communicate with an application server.
sap.app.description:
The SAPUI5 library contains classes that are mainly used in smart template applications, but can also be used in any Fiori/UI5 application
                   that uses the OData protocol to communicate with an application server.
